CIC, Blackstone to Buy Loan Assets From RBS, 21st Century Says

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-10-22T02:10:45Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-22/cic-blackstone-to-buy-loan-assets-from-rbs-21st-century-says.html
  China  Investment Corp. and
 Blackstone Group LP (BX)  will each invest 50 million pounds to
acquire part of the 1.4 billion pound real estate-related non-
performing loans package being sold by  Royal Bank of Scotland
Group Plc (RBS) , the 21st Century Business Herald reported today,
citing unnamed sources from the U.K. real estate industry.  China’s sovereign wealth fund CIC declined to comment.
Spokespeople from Blackstone and RBS didn’t answer phone calls
from Bloomberg News seeking comment.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Edward Johnson at 
 ejohnson28@bloomberg.net  